    "visualHierarchy": "Visual hierarchy is maintained using consistent typography and spacing. Section headers (e.g., \"Personal Details\") are slightly larger to set them apart from the individual settings.  The use of the `badge` component adds emphasis to the \"Verified ID\" status.  The use of `Neutral/neutral90` for primary text, `Neutral/neutral50` for secondary text, and `Primary/primary50` for actions creates a clear visual distinction between content and interactive elements. The consistent use of textStyles ensures a unified and professional look and feel."
  }
}
